		<title>15RAILWAYS</title>
		<content>                                       
 Only one railway line runs through    
 our area.                             
 This runs from Chesterfield to        
 Rotherham.                            
 The main purpose of the line is the   
 carrying of freight. Principally Merry
 Go Round coal trains, taking coal from
 pit to power station.                 
 This line has recently been           
 modernised.                           
 New colour light signalling and       
 continuous rail have been installed.  
 Barrow Hill engine sheds are situated 
 nearby.                               
 A branch goes from the main line to   
 Markham colliery, Colite works and    
 Bolsover colliery.                    
                                       
                                       
                                       
